1 consists of money distributed to the account under
2 IC 4-6-15-4(a)(3) and the balance of any opioid litigation
3 settlements remaining prior to the passage of P.L.72-2022. Money
4 in the account is continuously appropriated to the office of the
5 secretary of family and social services for treatment, education,
